text: Niscaya musalamana purusa, musalamana nari, imanadara purusa, imanadara nari, anugata purusa, anugata nari, satyabadi purusa, satyabadi nari, dhairyyasila purusa, dhairyyasila nari, binita purusa, binita nari, danasila purusa, danasila nari, roya palanakari purusa, roya palanakari nari, yaunanga hephayatakari purusa, , yaunanga hephayatakari nari, allahara adhika yikarakari purusa o yikarakari nari-tadera jan'ya allaha prastuta rekhechena ksama o mahapuraskara.
